{"tid":2330621,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"「寧願你自私一點」","createTime":"2020-12-18T07:24:15.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-18T07:30:51.000Z","uid":25558,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"4416ef3d1b58709b1c6ce9c46f925685edb1ba6f","tid":2330621,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-18T07:24:15.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201218/BBBIXEEQLREQ3MBREFVO4OSVVI/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201218%2FBBBIXEEQLREQ3MBREFVO4OSVVI%2F&d=PGKZrCzpIeFm7bz4D1EKrZLurRSHZiEGX9rhKonVocs%3D&h=6ef1b60d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201218%2FBBBIXEEQLREQ3MBREFVO4OSVVI%2F&h=1701428a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201218/BBBIXEEQLREQ3MBREFVO4OSVVI/</a><br />\n<br />\n「寧願你自私一點」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/Ed-Q1ZungFnQGOX9Ut9DA0HEbto=/1000x616/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/2LTPO5P3WVDW3H6UBGOUSLXYE4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FEd-Q1ZungFnQGOX9Ut9DA0HEbto%3D%2F1000x616%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2F2LTPO5P3WVDW3H6UBGOUSLXYE4.jpg&h=3d0a6203&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■「連儂聖誕樹」由《蘋果》Logo及memo紙砌成，為黎智英送上聖誕祝福。<br />\n<br />\n【讀者打氣】壹傳媒創辦人黎智英被關押半個月，未能與家人共度聖誕佳節。有市民直言他本不必受如斯苦難，「寧願你可自私一點」。有讀者借宋朝理學家邵雍的《心安吟》，勉勵黎保持心境平靜，即使被囚禁於斗室中，仍可感到「寬如天地間」。署名「支持你的香港人」來信稱黎年事已高，「最近天氣又再轉冷，你衣服夠暖嗎？晚上睡時被褥可耐寒嗎？」「蘋果讀者」稱黎本應退休享清福，弄孫為樂或環遊世界，「但你選擇愛香港、選擇留低、同一班無能力走的香港人面對最黑暗時期」。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/HBgSCz1c2JnRjWEnh-pApaXyQh4=/417x606/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/3JAZDK6H7BDSDDYFJ5LM5CJUZI.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FHBgSCz1c2JnRjWEnh-pApaXyQh4%3D%2F417x606%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2F3JAZDK6H7BDSDDYFJ5LM5CJUZI.gif&h=bbffda09&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■有讀者繪畫黎智英在《蘋果》黃傘下的背影，並寫上宋朝理學家邵雍的《心安吟》勉勵。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n天佑真香港人<br />\n<br />\n黎生：<br />\n<br />\n有次直播看到你被問及你頗擔心你家人，你不期然黯然神傷，是的，所有有良知的人都是只會想到別人、想到至親的人，希望上天保佑他們，也希望上天保佑真香港人，為香港付出和犧牲的所有人！<br />\n<br />\n支持你的一香港人上（節錄）<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n令我知道香港仍然很美<br />\n<br />\n親愛的肥佬黎：<br />\n<br />\n多謝你為民主、自由、言論及香港發聲及身體力行，多謝你無放棄香港、無放棄《蘋果》，多謝你面對各方面打壓、迫害仍然堅持，多謝你無畏無懼的精神，令我知道香港仍然很美。<br />\n<br />\n蘋果讀者上（節錄）<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n好人一生平安<br />\n<br />\n尊敬的黎智英先生：<br />\n<br />\n你不是一個人在孤軍作戰！相信公道自在人心！我會為你禱告，天主會保佑你的！好人會得到好的報應！好人一定一生平安！<br />\n<br />\n普通一名師奶上"},{"pid":"1ec43d44094184840d8b86a207958b468176aa47","tid":2330621,"uid":93986,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-18T07:30:51.000Z","msg":"走唔係自私 用佢既財力 去到海外組織 可以私了所有支那人"}]}